===Transitive verb===
'''thumb''' ([[thumbs]], [[thumbed]], [[thumbing]])

#To touch with the thumb.
#To turn the pages of (a book) in order to read it [[cursorily]].
#:''I thumbed through the book and decided not to bother reading it all.''

